commit.message:
MAINTAINERS: Add self and realphabetize.

	* MAINTAINERS: Add self and realphabetize.  Update entries
	for Dan Berlin, Chris Demetriou and Michael Matz.  Remove
	entry for a29k port maintainer.

From-SVN: r52908
